16
00:01:15,120 --> 00:01:16,070
Well...

17
00:01:18,230 --> 00:01:20,350
(If I want to return
to the 21st century soon,)

18
00:01:20,640 --> 00:01:21,960
(I can only take the initiative.)

19
00:01:21,960 --> 00:01:22,820
(Yanyu Pavilion)

20
00:01:22,830 --> 00:01:25,920
(The best way to approach others
is with kindness.)

21
00:01:26,140 --> 00:01:28,260
