22
00:01:33,120 --> 00:01:34,120
What are you doing here?

23
00:01:34,120 --> 00:01:36,000
This is the sugar water I made.
Please try it.

24
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:36,840
No need.

25
00:01:37,950 --> 00:01:40,150
(I anticipated this long ago.)

26
00:01:40,480 --> 00:01:42,790
(It's okay; I still have
a trick up my sleeve.)

27
00:01:43,220 --> 00:01:45,300
(Feigning a different intention)

28
00:01:46,430 --> 00:01:48,870
You want me to feed you personally,
right?

29
00:01:51,350 --> 00:01:52,200
What are you doing?

30
00:01:52,200 --> 00:01:53,790
I didn't mean it. Let me clean you up.

31
00:01:53,920 --> 00:01:55,790
Song Heng, throw her out.

32
00:01:56,430 --> 00:01:58,200
- Let me try again.
- Miss Xu, leave.

33
00:01:59,120 --> 00:02:00,230
Let me try again.

34
00:02:00,400 --> 00:02:01,640
Get a tailor to come tomorrow.

35
00:02:01,950 --> 00:02:03,790
- Yes.
- (A tailor?)

36
00:02:03,870 --> 00:02:04,710
(Alright.)

37
00:02:05,260 --> 00:02:07,310
(Switching places)

38
00:02:07,310 --> 00:02:09,430
Young Master, the tailor
for new clothes has arrived.

39
00:02:16,190 --> 00:02:18,240
