strange memories?)

40
00:02:18,400 --> 00:02:19,630
(Did I touch the wrong places?)

41
00:02:19,680 --> 00:02:20,750
(Could it be here?)

42
00:02:20,960 --> 00:02:21,800
(Here?)

43
00:02:21,840 --> 00:02:22,870
