52
00:02:43,190 --> 00:02:45,280
Miss Xu, why is it you?

53
00:02:48,630 --> 00:02:49,910
I'm making clothes.

54
00:02:52,030 --> 00:02:53,870
Stop trying to play tricks on me.

55
00:02:56,190 --> 00:02:57,680
I have no patience left.

56
00:03:02,960 --> 00:03:04,120
Seems you haven't learned

57
00:03:04,120 --> 00:03:05,150
