and see if we can get along.)

72
00:03:46,030 --> 00:03:47,750
Miss, you're amazing.

73
00:03:47,750 --> 00:03:49,120
You managed to find such a method.

74
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:50,360
A piece of cake.

75
00:03:50,670 --> 00:03:52,160
When I was in school,

76
00:03:52,170 --> 00:03:53,190
I often did this.

77
00:03:55,040 --> 00:03:56,770
Look at your dark circles.

78
00:03:56,960 --> 00:03:59,210
Mr. Yan didn't say
it had to be delivered today.

79
00:03:59,210 --> 00:04:01,080
How about we write it tomorrow?

80
00:04:01,250 --> 00:04:02,090
Sure.

81
00:04:11,000 --> 00:04:13,310
Miss, let's hurry back.

82
00:04:13,470 --> 00:04:16,480
It's been unsettling
in the mansion at night lately.

83
00:04:17,270 --> 00:04:18,480
Unsettling?

84
00:04:18,680 --> 00:04:20,070
I heard there are ghosts.

85
00:04:21,360 --> 00:04:22,920
How can there be ghosts in this world?

86
00:04:22,920 --> 00:04:23,760
Silly girl.

87
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:25,640
Stop!

88
00:04:29,630 --> 00:04:31,390
We are here on the orders of Father

89
00:04:31,680 --> 00:04:33,510
to apprehend you, you monster.

90
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:36,310
Who is she talking to?

91
00:04:38,270 --> 00:04:40,070
Is this the madam?

92
00:04:40,360 --> 00:04:42,120
I can't see clearly.

93
00:04:43,430 --> 00:04:45,120
What's going on?

94
00:04:50,120 --> 00:04:52,480
Miss, are we really going
to follow them?

95
00:04:52,480 --> 00:04:54,920
Don't be afraid.
I'll prove to you right now

96
00:04:54,920 --> 00:04:56,510
that there are no ghosts in this world.

97
00:05:01,270 --> 00:05:02,270
Madam?

98
00:05:02,920 --> 00:05:03,760
Madam?

99
00:05:22,980 --> 00:05:26,740
(Yanyu Pavilion)

100
00:05:28,510 --> 00:05:29,480
What time is it?

101
00:05:30,800 --> 00:05:31,640
Young Master,

102
00:05:31,830 --> 00:05:33,070
it's almost 11 pm.

103
00:05:34,750 --> 00:05:35,630
So late.

104
00:05:35,840 --> 00:05:36,870
She still hasn't returned?

105
00:05:37,270 --> 00:05:38,430
You mean

106
00:05:38,430 --> 00:05:39,720
Miss Xu, right?

107
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:40,840
Of course.

108
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:43,320
Yes.

109
00:05:43,510 --> 00:05:44,510
Miss Xu should still be

110
00:05:44,510 --> 00:05:45,870
with Madam,

111
00:05:45,870 --> 00:05:47,390
copying the rules.

112
00:05:47,870 --> 00:05:48,750
It's so late.

113
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:50,420
Why is she still at Muxi Pavilion?

114
00:05:53,390 --> 00:05:54,310
Let's go there.

115
00:05:54,430 --> 00:05:55,270
Hurry.

116
00:05:55,390 --> 00:05:56,230
Bring your sword.

117
00:06:02,310 --> 00:06:03,190
Where's my mother?

118
00:06:04,800 --> 00:06:05,920
I haven't seen her.

119
00:06:06,160 --> 00:06:07,720
Did Madam go to see the City Lord?

120
00:06:07,720 --> 00:06:09,480
That's impossible. I asked.

121
00:06:09,480 --> 00:06:10,830
They said Madam hasn't gone out.

122
00:06:10,830 --> 00:06:11,670
How about Xu Xinglan?

123
00:06:11,670 --> 00:06:13,750
I just saw Miss Xu and Madam
in the main hall.

124
00:06:13,750 --> 00:06:14,590
Let's go.

125
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:15,960
Let's go.

126
00:06:30,600 --> 00:06:31,750
Mother!

127
00:06:37,830 --> 00:06:38,830
