- Young Master, wait.

132
00:06:47,350 --> 00:06:48,490
Nanny Cui, perfect timing.

133
00:06:48,670 --> 00:06:50,150
Please explain to the Young Master.

134
00:06:50,150 --> 00:06:51,700
