137
00:06:57,100 --> 00:06:58,740
How am I supposed
to continue acting?

138
00:06:58,740 --> 00:06:59,580
Mother!

139
00:06:59,900 --> 00:07:00,860
- Brat.
- Madam!

140
00:07:00,860 --> 00:07:01,710
Why are you here?

141
00:07:01,710 --> 00:07:02,940
Miss Xu, are you alright?

142
00:07:03,820 --> 00:07:04,900
Oh, no.

143
00:07:04,900 --> 00:07:05,940
You're bleeding.

144
00:07:05,940 --> 00:07:06,980
What should we do?

145
00:07:08,060 --> 00:07:09,940
Look at what you've done to Xinglan.

146
00:07:10,410 --> 00:07:11,250
You...

147
00:07:12,620 --> 00:07:13,580
Yan.

148
00:07:13,620 --> 00:07:15,940
You know I'm interested in storytelling.

149
00:07:15,940 --> 00:07:16,840
I asked

150
00:07:16,860 --> 00:07:18,860
- Miss Xu to help me with this.
- Yes.

151
00:07:21,580 --> 00:07:23,700
Miss Xu, you mustn't tell anyone

152
00:07:23,700 --> 00:07:25,180
what you saw tonight.

153
00:07:28,580 --> 00:07:31,260
Madam has loved writing stories
since she was young.

154
00:07:31,260 --> 00:07:32,300
Every night,

155
00:07:32,300 --> 00:07:34,260
she thinks of new stories like this.

156
00:07:34,340 --> 00:07:35,660
If this gets out,

157
00:07:35,660 --> 00:07:37,620
it might tarnish Madam's reputation.

158
00:07:39,540 --> 00:07:40,780
So, that's how it is.

159
00:07:40,780 --> 00:07:41,900
Then may I ask if you can

160
00:07:41,900 --> 00:07:43,660
show me the stories?

161
00:07:43,660 --> 00:07:45,540
I can teach you something
even more fun.

162
00:07:47,820 --> 00:07:49,140
Something even more fun?

163
00:07:49,140 --> 00:07:50,020
That's ridiculous.

164
00:07:51,580 --> 00:07:52,700
If you hadn't come,

165
00:07:53,060 --> 00:07:54,860
we would have so much fun.

166
00:08:08,060 --> 00:08:08,900
How is she?

167
00:08:09,100 --> 00:08:10,020
Mr. Yan,

168
00:08:10,300 --> 00:08:11,540
I have given Miss Xu

169
00:08:11,540 --> 00:08:12,540
some calming medicine,

170
00:08:12,540 --> 00:08:13,580
and she's already asleep.

171
00:08:13,980 --> 00:08:15,220
For the wound on her neck,

172
00:08:15,220 --> 00:08:16,060
