173
00:08:16,060 --> 00:08:17,500
to ease the bleeding and bruising.

174
00:08:18,220 --> 00:08:19,060
Thank you.

175
00:08:19,980 --> 00:08:20,820
Please.

176
00:08:35,480 --> 00:08:37,100
