needs to be prepared.

177
00:08:37,100 --> 00:08:37,940
Hurry up.

178
00:08:37,950 --> 00:08:38,810
Yes.

179
00:08:40,040 --> 00:08:41,050
I'll step back now.

180
00:08:43,340 --> 00:08:46,490
Young Master, you were too ruthless.

181
00:08:47,330 --> 00:08:48,580
